      "cookedHtml": "<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=15\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> The Challenge</p>\n<p>NGOs and volunteer teams receive dozens of emails daily — donation offers, volunteer signups, medical supply requests. Most of these stay in inboxes, <strong>not in your <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> workflow</strong>.</p>\n<p>Manually copying emails into boards wastes time and causes missed tasks.</p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-231898-the-solution-email-to-tasks-for-mondaycomhttpsmondaycommarketplacelisting10000812emailtasks-for-mondaycomutm_sourcearticleutm_mediumreferralutm_campaignarticle_ngo-and-charity-teams_2025-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-231898-the-solution-email-to-tasks-for-mondaycomhttpsmondaycommarketplacelisting10000812emailtasks-for-mondaycomutm_sourcearticleutm_mediumreferralutm_campaignarticle_ngo-and-charity-teams_2025-1\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> The Solution: <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000812/emailtasks-for-mondaycom?utm_source=article&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=Article_NGO-and-Charity-Teams_2025\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Email to Tasks for monday.com</a></h3>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/5/d542f90ce3d958edf465f109824c121571384e42.jpeg\" title=\"Image 1 (3)\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/d/5/d542f90ce3d958edf465f109824c121571384e42_2_690x345.jpeg\" alt=\"Image 1 (3)\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Image 1 (3)</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 111 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>This browser extension lets you create fully structured <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> tasks <strong>directly from Gmail or Outlook</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Open the email</li>\n<li>Click the <strong>Email to Tasks</strong> icon</li>\n<li>Choose a board &amp; group</li>\n<li>Add assignee, status, due date, priority</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Create Task</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>No switching tabs. No manual entry. No context lost.</p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-231898-use-case-highlights-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-231898-use-case-highlights-2\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/globe_showing_europe_africa.png?v=15\" title=\":globe_showing_europe_africa:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":globe_showing_europe_africa:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Use Case Highlights</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/hospital.png?v=15\" title=\":hospital:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":hospital:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <em>“Need 30 tourniquets – Kharkiv Hospital”</em> → Add to <strong>Hospital Requests</strong>, mark <strong>Critical</strong>, assign to <strong>Logistics</strong></li>\n<li><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/person_raising_hand.png?v=15\" title=\":person_raising_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":person_raising_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <em>“I’d like to volunteer”</em> → Create task in <strong>Volunteers</strong>, assign to <strong>HR</strong></li>\n<li><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/money_bag.png?v=15\" title=\":money_bag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":money_bag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <em>“We’ll donate hygiene kits”</em> → Add to <strong>Donors &amp; Contributions</strong>, set due date, track donor</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-231898-why-ngo-teams-love-it-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-231898-why-ngo-teams-love-it-3\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/light_bulb.png?v=15\" title=\":light_bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":light_bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Why NGO Teams Love It</h3>\n<div class=\"md-table\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Without</th>\n<th>With Email to Tasks</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/cross_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":cross_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":cross_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Lost emails</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Tasks tracked</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/cross_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":cross_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":cross_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Manual work</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Instant creation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/cross_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":cross_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":cross_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Team silos</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Shared workflow</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div><hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-231898-secure-by-design-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-231898-secure-by-design-4\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/locked_with_key.png?v=15\" title=\":locked_with_key:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":locked_with_key:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Secure by Design</h3>\n<p>Uses official <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> APIs. Your data stays protected.</p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-231898-ready-to-try-5\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-231898-ready-to-try-5\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Ready to try?</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000812/emailtasks-for-mondaycom\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Install Email to Tasks for monday.com</a></strong><br />\nand turn your inbox into a mission-ready task hub.</p>\n<p>Full article - <a href=\"https://saasjet.com/blog/how-ngos-and-charity-teams-use-email-management-in-monday-com-to-stay-organized-and-responsive/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://saasjet.com/blog/how-ngos-and-charity-teams-use-email-management-in-monday-com-to-stay-organized-and-responsive/</a></p>"
